  faqs={[
    {
      question: "What is email automation for SaaS startups?",
      answer: "Email automation sends the right email to the right user at the right time without you pressing send. For SaaS startups, that means welcome emails when someone signs up, activation nudges when a user gets stuck, upgrade prompts when they hit a usage milestone, and recovery emails when a trial is about to expire. The good tools trigger emails based on what users do inside your product, not on a fixed timer. DigiStorms takes this a step further and generates the whole sequence with AI.",
